songs.lyrics:

I like this Asian Doll

Name ringing bells, I don’t fuck with hoes, these bitches fake as hell

Bentley tints on, Fendi prints on

But the pretty chopper hanging out that coupe

Bitch it’s King Kong!
Nicki really taught me how to do finesse
This is King Kong?
Bitches grew up fans, now they wanna sweat
Throwing shots, but it ain’t aiming, put that vest up on your chest
How many championships?
I don’t know, but we ain’t count, unless a check

[Bridge: Asian Doll & Nicki Minaj]
They need bitches like me!
They need real ass street bitches like me who gon’ smack the shit out of one of you dumb ass bitches

Chun Li!

[Chorus: Nicki Minaj]
Ayo, I been on, bitch, you been corn
Bentley tints on, Fendi prints on
I mean I been Storm, X-Men been formed
He keep on dialin' Nicki like the Prince song
I-I-I been on, bitch, you been corn
Bentley tints on, Fendi prints on
Ayo, I been north, Lara been Croft

[Outro: Nicki Minaj & Asian Doll]
I come alive, I, I'm always sky high
Designer thigh highs, it's my lifestyle
I come alive, I, I'm always sky high
Designer thigh highs, it's my lifestyle
I need a Mai Tai, so fuckin' sci-fi
Gimme the password to the fuckin' wifi
Queen of teens surfboard, tryna ride the wave
Edges laid, Asian paid, click my pic and save
I’m still the badder bitch, if I had a bald fade
Real bitches back in style and we come in all shades!
You know these niggas on the low
Goofy nigga wanna skeet, he tryna blow
songs.title: Chun-Li
